```
S3ObjectSummary s3ObjectSummary = new S3ObjectSummary();

    ObjectListing objects = new ObjectListing();
    objects.setBucketName(bucket);
    objects.setPrefix(prefix);

    List&lt;S3ObjectSummary&gt; objectSummaries = objects.getObjectSummaries();
    objectSummaries.add(s3ObjectSummary);
```

